# Ignore IDE-specific files and metadata
**/.classpath
**/.dockerignore
**/.env
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.project
**/.settings
**/.toolstarget
**/.vs
**/.vscode

# Ignore unnecessary user and build files
**/*.*proj.user
**/*.dbmdl
**/*.jfm

# Ignore Kubernetes/Helm configs (if not used inside the container)
**/azds.yaml
**/charts
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/values.dev.yaml

# Ignore build artifacts and dependencies
**/bin
**/obj
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/docker-compose*
**/Dockerfile*  # ❌ Keep this if you're using multi-stage builds outside Docker context

# Ignore logs and temporary files
**/*.log
**/logs
**/tmp
**/.temp

# Ignore documentation files (optional)
LICENSE
README.md

# ✅ Keep only necessary Git files for CI/CD
!**/.gitignore
!.git/HEAD
!.git/config
!.git/packed-refs
!.git/refs/heads/**
